snippet.title: Lockjaw: Robo-Royale - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Lockjaw: Robo-Royale, the successfully Kickstarter-funded local multiplayer robot brawler, comes out on Steam on Oct 21st, 2024!

Play it here! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2782270

Gather some friends and play local multiplayer or online with Steam Remote Play Together. Compete to win a Robo-Royale! 🤖🥊

Stay tuned for more about Lockjaw!
